properties.Name: DunBradstreetOperationsData
properties.Description: Details about company operations, such as the number of employees, facility type, location, and company description.

Columns.Name: DunsNumber
Columns.Description: Dun & Bradstreet (D&B) provides a D-U-N-S Number, a unique nine digit identification number, for each physical location of your business.

Columns.Name: ReportPurchaseDate
Columns.Description: The purchase date of the report.

Columns.Name: AsOfDate
Columns.Description: The as-of date of the operations data.

Columns.Name: OperationsDescription
Columns.Description:
A commentary of the company operations.

Ex:
Engaged in commercial lithographic printing (100%).
Terms are Net 30 days. Has 240 account(s). Sells to commercial concerns. Territory : United States.
Nonseasonal.

Columns.Name: EmployeesDescription
Columns.Description:
A description of the company employees.

Ex:
125 which includes officer(s). 110 employed here.

Columns.Name: FacilitiesDescription
Columns.Description:
A commentary of the company facilities

Ex:
Occupies premises in a one story cinder block building.

Columns.Name: LocationDescription
Columns.Description:
A commentary of the company location.

Ex:
Central business section on well traveled street.
